    <title>Windows 10自用应用集合</title>
    <url>/2adeb7d8.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Windows-10自用应用集合"><a href="#Windows-10自用应用集合" class="headerlink" title="Windows 10自用应用集合"></a>Windows 10自用应用集合</h1><h2 id="一，桌面软件"><a href="#一，桌面软件" class="headerlink" title="一，桌面软件"></a>一，桌面软件</h2><ol>
<li><p>镜像刻录 <a href="https://www.balena.io/etcher/">BalenaEtcher</a></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Earl9/picture/2021/01/27/01271249.png"></p>
</li>
<li><p>浏览器</p>
<ul>
<li><p><a href="https://www.google.cn/chrome/">Google chrome</a></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Earl9/picture/2021/01/27/01271251.png"></p>
</li>
<li><p><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/zh-cn/edge">Microsoft Edge</a></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Earl9/picture/2021/01/27/01271253.png"></p>
</li>
<li><p><a href="https://tools.shuax.com/edge/">Edge离线包</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>输入法 <a href="https://shurufa.baidu.com/">百度输入法</a></p>
</li>
<li><p>安全 <a href="https://www.huorong.cn/">火绒</a></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Earl9/picture/2021/01/27/01271257.png"></p>
</li>
<li><p>通讯</p>
<ul>
